Weather MAp

Overview
Weather Map is a mobile application designed to provide real-time weather information in a visually appealing and user-friendly way. The app is ideal for anyone who wants quick access to accurate weather updates, including:

Travelers planning their trips.
Outdoor enthusiasts preparing for activities.
Daily users who want to stay informed about local and global weather conditions.
Features
🌍 City Dropdown: Select a city to get the current weather details.
🌦 Real-Time Updates: Displays temperature, humidity, and weather conditions.
🖼 Dynamic Weather Icons: Visual representation of weather (sunny, rainy, cloudy, etc.).
📅 Daily Forecast: A snapshot of today’s weather.
🎨 Customizable Themes: User-friendly interface with an aesthetically pleasing design.
Target Audience
General Public: For casual weather checks.
Frequent Travelers: To plan ahead for weather conditions.
Outdoor Workers: For preparing work schedules and activities.
